Knight-right-at-the-Artists-Own-Gallery-on-Kingly-Street-in-London-September-1965-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他是 60 年代伦敦艺术界的一位有影响力的人物</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/damon-albarns-architect-and-influential-teacher-father-keith-has-died-3783438">达蒙·阿尔巴恩 (Damon Albarn) 的建筑师、“有影响力的老师”父亲基思 (Keith) 去世的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-right-at-the-Artists-Own-Gallery-on-Kingly-Street-in-London-September-1965-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Image.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="基思·奥尔本" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-right-at-the-Artists-Own-Gallery-on-Kingly-Street-in-London-September-1965-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Image.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-right-at-the-Artists-Own-Gallery-on-Kingly-Street-in-London-September-1965-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Image-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-right-at-the-Artists-Own-Gallery-on-Kingly-Street-in-London-September-1965-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Image-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-right-at-the-Artists-Own-Gallery-on-Kingly-Street-in-London-September-1965-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Image-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-right-at-the-Artists-Own-Gallery-on-Kingly-Street-in-London-September-1965-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Image-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-right-at-the-Artists-Own-Gallery-on-Kingly-Street-in-London-September-1965-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今天（8 月 13 日）宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/damon-albarn">Damon Albarn 的</a>建筑师父亲 Keith 去世，享年 85 岁。</p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blur-to-the-end-film-live-director-toby-l-wembley-future-3775212"><b>Blur 导演的新片《</b> <b><i>To The End》</i></b> <b>：“这是关于友谊和兄弟情谊的”</b></a></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a>主唱的父亲是一位艺术和设计专家，撰写了许多有关该主题的书籍和文章，并出现在许多电视和广播节目中。</p><p>基思 (Keith) 于 7 月 25 日被诊断出患有癌症后去世。根据<a href="https://www.thetimes.com/uk/obituaries/article/keith-albarn-obituary-artist-architect-and-father-of-damon-jgrmwd3mn" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《泰晤士报》</i></a>的讣告，基思以其对图案的学术研究而闻名，并且是 Minories 和科尔切斯特艺术中心的受托人。他是科尔切斯特学院艺术、设计和媒体学院的院长。 <a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-13674401/Blur-Live-Wembley-Stadium-review-Triumphant-comeback-writes-ADRIAN-THRILLS.html"><b>阅读更多</b></a></p><p>基思最初是一名建筑师，但最终成为一名艺术家。 <i>《泰晤士报》</i>将他描述为“城市地区感官太空时代游乐场的创造者和一位有影响力的老师”。</p><p>他在诺丁汉艺术学院就读时与妻子黑兹尔结婚。搬到伦敦后，基思继续在哈默史密斯艺术学院学习雕塑。</p><p>他与妻子 Hazel 和朋友 Ian Knight 在 Kingly Street 成立了“Keith Albarn and Partners Ltd”，并沉浸在摇摆不定的 60 年代伦敦艺术氛围中。</p><p>事实上，基思帮助组织了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yoko-ono">小野洋子在 Indica 画廊的</a>首次展览，她在那里第一次见到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3783458" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3783458" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3783458" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-left-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="英国艺术家基思·奥尔本" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-left-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-left-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-left-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-left-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-left-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/English-artist-Keith-Albarn-with-Ian-Knight-left-Photo-by-R.-McPhedran_Express_Hulton-Archive_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3783458" class="wp-caption-text">英国艺术家 Keith Albarn 和 Ian Knight（左）——图片来源：R. McPhedran/Express/Hulton Archive/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>开办公司后，基思彻底融入了伦敦艺术界，1966 年，他帮助在 Indica 画廊组织了 91 岁的小野洋子 (Yoko Ono) 的首次展览，小野洋子也是在那里第一次见到了约翰·列侬 (John Lennon)。 1967年，他还主办了马尔科姆·麦克拉伦的首次作品展。</p><p> Keith 与妻子 Hazel 育有两个孩子，分别是 56 岁的英国流行音乐传奇达蒙和 53 岁的艺术家女儿杰西卡。</p><p>您可以在这里看到一些对基思的致敬：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Keith Albarn 是一位深入参与 60 年代迷幻运动的建筑师和设计师：他设计了 Fun Palace，管理 Soft Machine，参与早期 Pink Floyd 演出，并在 Indica 画廊组织了小野洋子的首次展览，她在那里认识了列侬。安息吧基思<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f494.png" alt="💔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/7f3OmsUZ3s">pic.twitter.com/7f3OmsUZ3s</a></p><p> — 达蒙·阿尔本非官方 (@DamonUnofficial) <a href="https://